				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">One way is by rewriting the nametable in invisible areas to all-black tiles. Another way is by making one of the palettes all-black (or at least much darker) and rewriting the attribute table. NetHack does something similar with the single layer of monospaced text that a PC terminal provides.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

