				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I don't see any other options other than the ones tepples mentioned, along with black sprites to make the illuminated areas rounder. If you go with the attribute table solution, you'll end up needing a lot of sprites, because the basic units you can hide/show are 16x16-pixels instead of the 8x8-pixels you can do with the name tables.</div>

